# Redirect URI Configuration (Choose ONE option below)

# OPTION 1: Local Development
# REDIRECT_URI=https://localhost:3000/auth/callback

# OPTION 2: Ngrok Tunnel (Recommended for testing)
# REDIRECT_URI=https://your-ngrok-url.ngrok.io/auth/callback

# OPTION 3: Production Domain  
# REDIRECT_URI=https://yourdomain.com/auth/callback

# OPTION 4: Vercel Deploy
# REDIRECT_URI=https://yourappname.vercel.app/auth/callback

# OPTION 5: Railway/Render
# REDIRECT_URI=https://yourapp.railway.app/auth/callback

# AFTER CHOOSING ONE ABOVE:
# 1. Go to TikTok Developer Console: https://developers.tiktok.com
# 2. Select your app and go to "Login Kit for Web"
# 3. Add your chosen REDIRECT_URI
# 4. Save configuration
# 5. Run the launch script